### Module - Get Modules by Course ID
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/courses/{{courseId}}/modules
Accept: application/json

### Module - Create New Module for Course
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/courses/{{courseId}}/modules
Authorization: Bearer {{instructor_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Module 2: Basics",
    "description": "Covers the basic concepts and fundamentals."
}

### Module - Update Module by ID
@moduleId = fb456a6b-606a-4a18-90dd-af5bf5e19776
PUT {{API_HostAddress}}/modules/{{moduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{instructor_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Module 2: Basics - Updated",
    "description": "Updated basic concepts and fundamentals."
}

### Module - Delete Module by ID
DELETE {{API_HostAddress}}/modules/{{moduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{instructor_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Lesson - Get Lessons by Module ID
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/modules/{{moduleId}}/lessons
Accept: application/json

### Lesson - Create New Lesson for Module
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/modules/{{moduleId}}/lessons
Authorization: Bearer {{instructor_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Lesson 4: Lets Get Started",
    "description": "Introduction to getting started with the module.",
    "contentType": "video",
    "contentUrl": "https://example.com/lesson4-getting-started.mp4",
    "orderIndex": 4
}

### Lesson - Update Lesson by ID
